videos.headline: Appalachian State pulls some trickery on this 43-yard TD pass
videos.description: Appalachian State WR Malik Williams gets the ball and throws to  fellow receiver Thomas Hennigan for a 43-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Appalachian State pulls some trickery on this 43-yard TD pass) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Appalachian State's Steven Jones. comes up big with pick-six
videos.description: Steven Jones Jr. picks off the pass and takes it over 40 yards the other way for a Mountaineers touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Steven Jones Jr. scores Defensive touchdown vs. Arkansas State) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arkansas State gets on the board with Emmanuel Stevenson's 7-yard receiving TD
videos.description: Layne Hatcher finds Emmanuel Stevenson for a 7-yard touchdown to put the Red Wolves on the board.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Emmanuel Stevenson hauls it in for 7-yard Receiving touchdown) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Layne Hatcher's 2nd passing TD ties the game
videos.description: Layne Hatcher throws a dart to Ross Painter for a 20-yard touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Layne Hatcher throws 20-yard TD Pass vs. Appalachian State) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Appalachian State reclaim the lead on Nathaniel Noel's 18-yard TD
videos.description: Nathaniel Noel turn on the burners and hits the corner for an 18-yard rushing touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Nathaniel Noel runs for 18-yard Rushing touchdown) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Appalachian State extends lead on Brice's TD pass to Gibbs
videos.description: Chase Brice dumps it off to Miller Gibbs for a 10-yard Mountaineers touchdown.

tracking.trackingName: NCF_One-Play (Chase Brice with 10-yard touchdown Pass to Miller Gibbs vs. Arkansas State) 2021/11/06 ESHEET

videos.headline: Camerun Peoples burns past the Arkansas State defense on this TD
videos.description: Camerun Peoples shows his speed as he runs past the Red Wolves' defense for a 27-yard touchdown.
